{"tha-ap36:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap36:0.2":"Kundadhanavagga ","tha-ap36:0.3":"Kaludayittheraapadana ","tha-ap36:1.1":"“Padumuttarabuddhassa, ","tha-ap36:1.2":"lokajetthassa tadino; ","tha-ap36:1.3":"Addhanam patipannassa, ","tha-ap36:1.4":"carato carikam tada. ","tha-ap36:2.1":"Suphullam padumam gayha, ","tha-ap36:2.2":"uppalam mallikancaham; ","tha-ap36:2.3":"Paramannam gahetvana, ","tha-ap36:2.4":"adasim satthuno aham. ","tha-ap36:3.1":"Paribhunji mahaviro, ","tha-ap36:3.2":"paramannam subhojanam; ","tha-ap36:3.3":"Tanca puppham gahetvana, ","tha-ap36:3.4":"janassa sampadassayi. ","tha-ap36:4.1":"Ittham kantam piyam loke, ","tha-ap36:4.2":"jalajam pupphamuttamam; ","tha-ap36:4.3":"Sudukkaram katam tena, ","tha-ap36:4.4":"yo me puppham adasidam. ","tha-ap36:5.1":"Yo pupphamabhiropesi, ","tha-ap36:5.2":"paramannancadasi me; ","tha-ap36:5.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap36:5.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap36:6.1":"‘Dasa attha cakkhattum so, ","tha-ap36:6.2":"devarajjam karissati; ","tha-ap36:6.3":"Uppalam padumancapi, ","tha-ap36:6.4":"mallikanca taduttari. ","tha-ap36:7.1":"Assa punnavipakena, ","tha-ap36:7.2":"dibbagandhasamayutam; ","tha-ap36:7.3":"Akase chadanam katva, ","tha-ap36:7.4":"dharayissati tavade. ","tha-ap36:8.1":"Pancavisatikkhattunca, ","tha-ap36:8.2":"cakkavatti bhavissati; ","tha-ap36:8.3":"Pathabya rajjam pancasatam, ","tha-ap36:8.4":"vasudham avasissati. ","tha-ap36:9.1":"Kappasatasahassamhi, ","tha-ap36:9.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap36:9.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap36:9.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap36:10.1":"Sakakammabhiraddho so, ","tha-ap36:10.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap36:10.3":"Sakyanam nandijanano, ","tha-ap36:10.4":"natibandhu bhavissati. ","tha-ap36:11.1":"So paccha pabbajitvana, ","tha-ap36:11.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap36:11.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap36:11.4":"nibbayissatinasavo. ","tha-ap36:12.1":"Patisambhidamanuppattam, ","tha-ap36:12.2":"katakiccamanasavam; ","tha-ap36:12.3":"Gotamo lokabandhu tam, ","tha-ap36:12.4":"etadagge thapessati. ","tha-ap36:13.1":"Padhanapahitatto so, ","tha-ap36:13.2":"upasanto nirupadhi; ","tha-ap36:13.3":"Udayi nama namena, ","tha-ap36:13.4":"hessati satthu savako’. ","tha-ap36:14.1":"Rago doso ca moho ca, ","tha-ap36:14.2":"mano makkho ca dhamsito; ","tha-ap36:14.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap36:14.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap36:15.1":"Tosayincapi sambuddham, ","tha-ap36:15.2":"atapi nipako aham; ","tha-ap36:15.3":"Pasadito ca sambuddho, ","tha-ap36:15.4":"etadagge thapesi mam. ","tha-ap36:16.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap36:16.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap36:16.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap36:17.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma kaludayi thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap36:18.1":"Kaludayittherassapadanam catuttham. "}